      "chapterUid": 21,
      "range": "8536-8584",
      "markText": "中国人给动植物取名字，向来不严谨，不像西方人，给动植物命名，有严格的科学界定，有种属、科目之分。",
      "totalCount": 128,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=684726&chapterUid=21&rangeStart=8536&rangeEnd=8584",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/268321905a72b62684307bf?chapterUid=21&rangeStart=8536&rangeEnd=8584"
    },
